org.codice.ddf.catalog.async.data.api.internal

Interface ProcessUpdateItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProcessItem, ProcessResourceItem

    public interface ProcessUpdateItem
extends ProcessResourceItem

    This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library.

    The ProcessUpdateItem represents the data that will be processed by the PostProcessPlugins after a Metacard has been updated in the catalog.
